subject: Golf
Canadian Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Robert Allenby withdrew from the Canadian Open in Oakville, Ontario, after splitting with his caddie, Mick Middlemo, in the first round. Chad Campbell held a two-stroke lead at nine-under 63.
